Russia Offers Tax Breaks to Venture Investors, Kommersant Says

-- B y   Y u l i y a   F e d o r i n o v a
-- 
2011-12-06T04:21:15Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-06/russia-offers-tax-breaks-to-venture-investors-kommersant-says.html
Russia  may offer tax breaks for long-
term venture investors, who buys into shares of so-called
innovation companies,  Kommersant  reported today, citing a
Ministry of Economy draft decree.  Such investors may not have to pay income tax after 2016,
when they sell the stock, Kommersant said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Yuliya Fedorinova in Moscow at 
 yfedorinova@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
John Viljoen at 
 jviljoen@bloomberg.net  